{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"16503","heading":"Sugar ethanol loan guarantee program","label":"16503 Sugar ethanol loan guarantee program","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/ch149/schXIV","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextTitle XIV, referred to in subsec. (a), is title XIV of , , , which enacted subchapter XIII of this chapter and .Pub. L. 109–58119 Stat. 1061section 13557 of this titleAug. 8, 2005"],"amendments":["References in TextTitle XIV, referred to in subsec. (a), is title XIV of , , , which enacted subchapter XIII of this chapter and .Pub. L. 109–58119 Stat. 1061section 13557 of this titleAug. 8, 2005"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Funds may be provided for the cost (as defined in ) of loan guarantees issued under title XIV to carry out commercial demonstration projects for ethanol derived from sugarcane, bagasse, and other sugarcane byproducts.section 661a of title 21See References in Text note below.1","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Demonstration projects","label":"b Demonstration projects","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary may issue loan guarantees under this section to projects to demonstrate commercially the feasibility and viability of producing ethanol using sugarcane, sugarcane bagasse, and other sugarcane byproducts as a feedstock.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Requirements","label":"c Requirements","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the project design has been validated through the operation of a continuous process facility;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the project has been subject to a full technical review;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the project, with the loan guarantee, is economically viable; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"there is a reasonable assurance of repayment of the guaranteed loan.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Limitations","label":"d Limitations","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Maximum guarantee","label":"1 Maximum guarantee","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"may be issued for up to 80 percent of the estimated cost of a project; but","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"shall not exceed $50,000,000 for any 1 project.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":"Additional guarantees","label":"2 Additional guarantees","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":"In general","label":"A In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F2%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"up to 80 percent of the excess of actual project costs; but","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F2%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"not to exceed 15 percent of the amount of the original loan guarantee.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":"Principal and interest","label":"B Principal and interest","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s16503/d/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs16503%2Fd%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Subject to subparagraph (A), the Secretary shall guarantee 100 percent of the principal and interest of a loan guarantee made under subparagraph (A).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
